Author: pandaDesu
Text: Hey just want to say that I love Wonder Girls and listened to Sunmi's Full Moon EP years ago but haven't really kept up with k-pop in a while, so I checked her out again after reading this post and oh man Warning EP is actually really good?? I love Siren and Curve especially!  Thank you for reminding me of her, I wouldn't have checked her out again if you hadn't posted.

Author: TreatyPie
Text: I wasn’t familiar with her but looked her up because of your post. She looks much healthier and I’m so happy that that is healing to you.     I know I’m just another internet stranger but as someone with a younger teenage sister that idolizes Asian pop singers, i think your reasoning is very mature and I’m proud of you!
